-- Author Scott Martelle Discusses History of Detroit (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-07-22T13:32:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-22/author-scott-martelle-discusses-history-of-detroit-audio-.html
Scott Martelle, author of "Detroit: 
A Biography," discusses the city's history and issues that may 
have led to its bankruptcy filing. Martelle talked with 
Bloomberg's Pimm Fox and  Carol Massar  on Bloomberg Radio's 
"Taking Stock" on July 19th.    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 09:16
 